name: dying at spirit halloween
description: dress up like joe dirt and die outside of a pop-up halloween store in your hometown. let it be the climax to your pitiful existence. look into the vacant eyes of indifferent employees as they watch you writhe. as they watch your arteries close one final time. let them give your family a 20% off coupon for the trouble. die doing what you love in an irrelevant costume and hope that your family can return it for store credit.
